common.privacyInfo:
{projectName} respects your privacy!
{projectName} (hereafter "we") respects the privacy of its users (hereafter "you"). In order to provide you with applications and services, we will collect some of your personal data. Please read this agreement carefully before using our services to understand how your personal information will be collected, stored, used and disclosed. We do not sell, distribute and share your personal information, your trust is the cornerstone of our success

collect information

Our services may require you to register for an account. When you register, we will request the use of your personal information, including your name, email address, phone number or credit card information. When you use our products, we may collect information about the products you use and learn how you use our services. We need your personal information, including your name, address, email address and phone number.
·Product Registration
·Create an account
·Information subscription
·feedback
·Request for service
·User research
·Information usage

We will use your personal information in the following situations:

·Provide you with detailed information about application upgrades, services, news, emails, and improvements about our applications.
·Provide you with advanced service features that you may be interested in.
·To meet your needs, assist us in developing better products and services.
·Allows you to purchase and download products, including using services or accessing actions of your choice.
·Help you find software, service or application information quickly.
·With your consent, you have the right to participate in interactive features in our service.
·Notify you of product and service updates.
·We may use your information to contact you for market research.

Personal information security:

We are always committed to protecting the information security of our users. In order to prevent unauthorized access, information leakage, loss and destruction, and to ensure that the information will be used for the correct purpose, we will take corresponding measures from manual maintenance, technical and management level to ensure information security.
